high_descs: Turn right, then left to exit the room, then right again until reaching the cabinet on the left, going all the way towards the wall.
Remove a mango from the upper cabinet nearest the corner.
Turn back from where you came and stop at the fridge.
Place the mango in the fridge, let it cool, then retrieve it.
Place the mango on the drainboard next to the sink.
